name: Issue 5.5
description:
Our very first printed issue will be a 16 page, fully colour, A5 zine featuring everything that is good in the world which is digital. It will feature numerous artists who have been inspired by the computer from a variety of disciplines from, gif animators, textile designers, musicians, illustrators, glitch artists, photographers and more.

It will also feature a screen printed packaging & all orders will be sent an exclusive digital zine at some stage during the summer.

The zine will be finished and shipped off by the 30th of March by the latest, shipping is global.

Delayed till the 7th of April due to printing issues.
